// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0668 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 2b17af1d-2982-54b2-a3cd-b4907789786a

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.10*")
